            <bug_when>2011-11-10 16:43:58 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>The includeFile method of qx.bom.Stylesheet is responsible for inlcuding CSS files. For that, it allows to use resource ID&#39;s which will be resolved by the resource manager. As this is a bom class which should be as lightweight as possible, the inclusion of the resource manager is not a good idea so we should deprecate that.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
